Ask HN: Best way/apps to manage & free up macOS disk space?
text:
This is super strange. All I've ever used my mac for is web dev.

Yet I'm constantly running out of space.

For example in Storage under System Information, it shows that "Other" takes up 350GB of data.

What are some good ways (eg trusted paid apps) to free up MacOS disk space? Thanks!
